OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing this evening, some of these
OL,7,Fmay be heavy and thundery especially
OL,8,Fin the east with some sunny interludes
OL,9,Fin-between showers. Drier conditions
OL,10,Fto follow overnight as showers
OL,11,Fgradually fade. A chilly night
OL,12,Fespecially in rural spots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA dry start for most on
OL,15,FWednesday with sunny spells in the
OL,16,Fmorning. Showers developing from late
OL,17,Fmorning, these may be heavy and turn
OL,18,Fthundery by the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
